title: ARTISTRY Collapsible Dog Bowl Pack of 2 - Portable Travel Bowl for Small Pets, Silicone, Foldable with Metal Hook (Red/Yellow)

description: Product Description STRONG COLORED CARABINER Simply slip the silicone holder and clip it onto your bag or day pack.
